dialog.body: Hello, thank you for contacting Old Stone Auto Insurance. My name is Arthur Davis. May I have your name, please?
Nice to meet you, Amanda. Can you please provide me with your policy number for verification purposes?
Of course. My policy number is five six nine zero two.
Thank you, Amanda. Additionally, could you please confirm the make and model of the vehicle involved in the incident?
The vehicle is a two zero one nine Honda Civic.
Thank you for the information. We will start processing your claim. Is there anything else you would like to add before we proceed further?
No, that would be all. Thank you.
You're welcome, Amanda. Thank you for reaching out to us. We will keep you updated on the progress of your claim. Have a great day!
